OL,3,CAlabama executes first death row
OL,4,Cinmate by nitrogen gas
OL,6,FAlabama has become the first US state
OL,7,Fto execute a man using nitrogen gas.
OL,9,FConvicted murderer Kenneth Smith, 58,
OL,10,Flost two final appeals to prevent the
OL,11,Fexecution. On Thursday, the US Supreme
OL,12,FCourt denied a last-minute appeal from
OL,13,FSmith's attorneys who argued it was an
OL,14,Funusual and cruel punishment.
OL,16,FHis time of death was 8.25pm local
OL,17,Ftime on Thursday (2.25am GMT),
OL,18,Faccording to a news release from the
OL,19,FGovernor of Alabama.
