OL,3,CAlabama executes first death row
OL,4,Cinmate by nitrogen gas
OL,6,FSmith inhaled pure nitrogen gas
OL,7,Fthrough a face mask causing oxygen
OL,8,Fdeprivation.
OL,10,FAlabama had tried and failed to
OL,11,Fexecute Smith in 2022 by using lethal
OL,12,Finjection.
OL,14,FInside the chamber with him was his
OL,15,Fspiritual adviser, Rev. Jeff Hood who
OL,16,Fearlier on Thursday said Smith ate a
OL,17,Ffinal meal of T-bone steak, hash
OL,18,Fbrowns, toast, and eggs slathered in
OL,19,FA1 steak sauce.
