OL,6,FThe American Veterinary Medical
OL,7,FAssociation in 2020 euthanasia
OL,8,Fguidelines wrote nitrogen hypoxia is
OL,9,Fnot an acceptable euthanasia method
OL,10,Ffor most mammals because the anoxic
OL,11,Fenvironment is "distressing".
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, both the US Supreme
OL,14,FCourt and 11th Circuit Court of
OL,15,FAppeals said they would not block the
OL,16,Fexecution despite Smiths' pleas for it
OL,17,Fto intervene.
